channel.title: How do I stop this error, and what is it?
channel.description:
Hi, here is my error ( Ip's have been changed for privacy ):
[CODE]Connection accepted from 217.xxx.30.xxx: 1872. Client type: high memory version UserId: 82128902 joker lt is signing onto server. LOADED: 3 Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NumberFormatException: For input string: "c " at java.lang.NumberFormatException.forInputString(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Unknown Source) at client.initialize(client.java:13882) at PlayerHandler.process(PlayerHandler.java:204) at server.main(server.java:50) Connection accepted from cpe-x2-185-226-xxx.tampabay.res.rr.com: 1880. Client type: high memory version UserId: 15463984 xx pure xx is signing onto server. [client-5-xx pure xx]: xx pure xx is already online. Connection accepted from xxx.117.30.xxx: 1874. Client type: high memory version UserId: 82128902 joker lt is signing onto server. [client-6-joker lt]: joker lt is already online. Connection accepted from 87.xx.27.x: 52713. Client type: high memory version UserId: 82128902 g o d pk is signing onto server. [client-7-g o d pk]: g o d pk is already online. Connection accepted from x1-x-xx-0c-f6-23-c6-xx.k274.xxxspeed.dk: 51057.[/CODE]
At first my server is okay , but after a while, I get that error, everyone gets kicked off, and it says they are already logged in.
How do I fix this?
Thanks
